snippet.title: Klang Official Steam Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Get Klang on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/412660

Klang is an innovative take on traditional rhythm games that pushes the genre beyond pressing buttons to tempo into a world of fast-paced exploration, platforming and combat. Set to the music of legendary EDM composer, bLiNd, Klang is an adrenaline rush sure to challenge even the most skilled of multitaskers.

Follow Klang
Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/tinimations
Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/tinimations
Website: http://www.tinimations.com
